stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> ProbeStandard
    ProbeStandard: detect @ offset 0
    ProbeStandard --> StandardOK: header decrypts
    ProbeStandard --> StandardFail: no valid header

    StandardOK: outer (standard) volume mounted
    StandardOK --> MaybeHidden

    state MaybeHidden <<choice>>
    MaybeHidden --> ProbeTrailingModern: try_hidden=True
    MaybeHidden --> [*]: try_hidden=False

    ProbeTrailingModern: detect @ (vol_size - 65536)
    ProbeTrailingModern --> HiddenModernOK: modern VeraCrypt header
    ProbeTrailingModern --> ProbeTrailingLegacy: no modern header

    ProbeTrailingLegacy: detect @ (vol_size - 131072)
    ProbeTrailingLegacy --> HiddenLegacyOK: legacy TrueCrypt header
    ProbeTrailingLegacy --> NoHidden: no header found

    HiddenModernOK: hidden volume unlocked (modern)
    HiddenLegacyOK: hidden volume unlocked (legacy)
    NoHidden: only outer volume is present

    StandardFail --> [*]: abort
    HiddenModernOK --> [*]
    HiddenLegacyOK --> [*]
    NoHidden --> [*]
